        {
            "title": "荃灣昌榮路迴旋處輕貨鏟上花槽 司機一度被困",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ce8b51fe64b041bd3412ac23a4a87b46/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032212055511124.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員到場調查。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣昌榮路迴旋處往荃灣方向，今（22日）早上11時26分，一部輕型貨車失控鏟上花槽石壆，司機報稱被困，救護員接報到場，司機已自行行出車廂，他沒有受傷，拒絕送院。警方正調查意外原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152282/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"輕貨鏟上花槽石壆。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82020ab94e4cd7806a260666b57e4f4d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250322_115544870.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        輕貨鏟上花槽石壆。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152283/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4c84a73a042b7e586d2fabc01e0a5bfc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250322_115544870_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059630/即時-港聞-荃灣昌榮路迴旋處輕貨鏟上花槽-司機一度被困",
