        {
            "title": "邁阿密大師賽｜祖高域贏波平拿度紀錄 殺入第3圈止3連敗：想證明我仲打得",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3199c8d9e598217d21828742449f3a54/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032211171661792.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周五邁阿密網球大師賽男單次圈賽事，祖高域直落兩盤輕鬆擊敗土方凜輝，躋身第3圈並且收穫個人第410場大師賽勝仗平拿度的歷史紀錄。此子於過去兩項賽事均一輪遊，今仗終重返勝軌止3連敗，他喜言想證明自己仍可打出高水平網球。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b019153458e0a93b2a688d8f05ccee5/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279192.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51fc3e9d8447e1857ced690f88d0a279/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279195.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/665a8feefa4f75b5bc90a7c4e799b1cb/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279167.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62deb10c926e5e00977a9f3f77434be4/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279278.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2cb6645e81eb98848372835044377d8d/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279193.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖高域殺入第3圈。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"土方凜輝。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2971b22565ae96919c16c13ceb6bd88/2025-03/GettyImages-2206279323.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        土方凜輝。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>祖高域贏波平拿度紀錄</h2>\n<p>今場面對澳洲的土方凜輝，4號種子祖高域打得十分輕鬆，首盤即橫掃局數6:0先下一城，次盤雙方拉鋸要進入搶七，最終祖高域在搶七階段再有壓倒性優勢，以7:6(7:1)再贏一盤，盤數2:0晉級。今場奏捷後，祖高域取得生涯第410場大師賽勝利，追平西班牙名將拿度並列史上最多，並有望於下輪獨佔第一。\n\n</p><h2>止3連敗證明自己</h2>\n<p>37歲的祖高域今年開季不順，於澳網四強因傷退賽，之後在多哈和印第安泉網賽都意外一輪遊，今場總算終止3連敗，他矢言：「我想向自己和其他人證明，我仍然有能力打出高水平的比賽。我在過去兩個賽都首輪落敗，所以我真的很渴望在邁阿密的第一場比賽中取得勝利。上站比賽後我有2周時間備戰，這對我今天的表現有正面影響，我對自己在球場上的感覺和表現非常滿意。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059621/即時-體育-邁阿密大師賽-祖高域贏波平拿度紀錄-殺入第3圈止3連敗-想證明我仲打得",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-22 12:11:48",
